        </item>
        <item>
            <title>純電 Alfa Romeo Junior 香港試駕，集操控樂趣與舒適感於一身的小型 SUV</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/alfa-romeo-junior-hk-testdrive/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=alfa-romeo-junior-hk-testdrive</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/alfa-romeo-junior-hk-testdrive/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 04:44:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Alfa Romeo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[junior]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[愛快羅密歐]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297848</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>上個月在香港正式亮相的小型 SUV Alfa Romeo Junior 是該意大利汽車品牌推出的首款純電動車，這款車最初命名為 &#8220;Milano&#8221;，但因意大利政府反對使用城市名稱，最終更名為 &#8220;Junior&#8221;，藉此向經典車型致敬。這款去年在歐洲開售，市場反應甚佳的緊湊型 SUV，香港將會是<span lang="ZH-TW">亞太地區首個推出</span><span lang="ZH-TW">的市場，而 </span>unwire.hk 剛剛亦安排了本地的 Alfa Romeo Junior 實車測試。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_1528180-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_1528180-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_1528180.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152928-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152928-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152928.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>作為 Alfa Romeo 進軍電動車市場的第一步，Junior 採用 Stellantis 集團的 e-CMP 平台，與 Jeep Avenger 和 Peugeot e-2008 等車型共享技術基礎，並提供純電 / 混能版本車型選擇。外觀設計上，車長僅 4,173mm 的 Junior 延續了 Alfa Romeo 的經典美學，前方鬼面罩保留標誌性的 Scudetto 三角盾形設計，更加上品牌潦草字樣更顯獨特。Junior 搭配 「3+3」 全 LED 矩陣頭燈散發現代科技感。後門採用隱藏式後門把手，車尾「coda tronca」陡峭的線條十分令人熟悉，倒 U 型一體式尾燈與頭燈設計相呼應，黑色飾條環繞尾燈的車尾則從 Giulia TZ 汲取靈感，具有更強的視覺層次。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299036 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170589-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170589-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170589.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299053 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170592-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170592-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170592.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Junior 擁有經特別設計的空氣動力學車身及輕量化設計，全車僅重 1,545KG，為同級 SUV 車中最輕巧的車款，具備同級最佳的動態性能、操控性和靈活性。動力方面，Alfa Romeo Junior Launch 及 Sport Edition 均搭載 156 匹馬力的馬達，最大扭力 260Nm，0-100 km/h 加速約 9 秒。前輪驅動的 Junior 並搭載 54kWh 鋰電池。Launch / Sport Edition 的 WLTP 續航里程可達 410 公里，在城市路況下更可達到 590 公里。充電方面，直流快充則支援最高 100kW 功率，從 20% 到 80% 充電約需 30 分鐘。</p><figure id="attachment_1299071" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1299071" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299071" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170581-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170581-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170581.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1299071" class="wp-caption-text"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299040 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170622-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170622-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170622.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></figcaption></figure><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299046" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151937-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151937-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151937.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299048 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170606-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170606-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170606.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299041" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151052-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151052-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151052.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Junior 的行李廂容量達 400 公升，後座放平後可擴充至 1,265 公升，在同級車中頗具實用性。</p><p>內櫳方面，Junior 駕駛艙充滿品牌特色，配備雙 10.25 吋螢幕：儀表顯示器採用經典「望遠鏡」造型，中央觸控螢幕角度略向駕駛傾斜，提升顯覺效果及操作便利性。空調出風口靈感來自 Quadrifoglio 的四葉草標誌，Sport Edition 更會提供鑲空設計的 Sabelt 運動座椅，可選紅黑皮革與麂皮材質，增添豪華氛圍。Alfa D.N.A 駕駛模式（Dynamic、Natural、Advanced Efficiency），讓駕駛者根據不同需要調整油門反應與轉向手感，此外，它亦提供動能回收開關功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151842-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151842-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151842.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299042" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151607-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151607-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151607.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152252-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152252-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152252.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299038 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170615-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170615-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170615.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299037 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170599-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170599-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170599.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299049 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170651-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170651-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170651.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">中控下方的置物空間設有無線充電板及 2 個 USB 取電介面。</p><h2 data-start="0" data-end="25"><strong data-start="0" data-end="25">試駕體驗：輕巧靈活，富操控樂趣而不失舒適感</strong></h2><p data-start="27" data-end="166">今次試駕嘅 Junior 是一款相當小巧的 SUV，車長約 4.1 米、車寬約 1.7 米、高度約 1.53 米，短小的車身非常適合市區行駛，亦可隨意進出任何停車場。今次試駕路線包括港島西區、南區淺水灣道同埋域多利道等彎多路窄嘅地方。Junior 車身動態相當靈活，軚盤的指向性亦非常準確，很適合應付這類雙線雙程、還可能要防備如巴士、旅遊巴等大車偷位的路段。這款車雖然並非以性能作為賣點，但勝在操控方面非常出色，懸掛亦調校得宜，喺凹凸不平嘅路面上行駛，發揮很好的濾震，即使在應付中低速的連續彎位時，車身晃動亦沒有很明顯。</p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152217-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152217-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152217.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299039 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170617-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170617-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170617.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p data-start="27" data-end="166">動力方面，廠方公佈 Junior 馬力為 156 匹，試駕的時候它的電馬達提供嘅即時動力和加速感輕鬆超越 3500cc 級別的汽油車，無論在置富上斜定係需要加速超車，車內載滿乘客亦不會覺得動力不足。至於駕駛模式方面，呢部車有三個模式— Dynamic、Natural 和 Advanced Efficiency，在不同情況下可以切換使用。Dynamic 模式下，電門反應會更快，加速感較強，但唔會即刻變咗一架賽車，感覺上仍然很溫和，唔會太過激烈。Advanced Efficiency 模式以節能為主會更加慳電，車輛會回收動能，減低能源消耗。整體來講，這部車的電門反應唔會太過敏感，駕駛感覺偏柔，適合長時間駕駛，富有駕駛樂趣和舒適感並存。</p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151715-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151715-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151715.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151728-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151728-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151728.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p data-start="27" data-end="166">外觀方面，它的設計很有科技感，特別係個倒三角色鬼面罩和 LED 頭燈，睇落唔單止時尚更有獨特性，不容易同其他市面上嘅電動車撞樣。美中不足的是此車後座較窄，後座中間設有馬鞍位，如果成人坐喺後排中間，應該會覺得有啲辛苦，比較適合小朋友。總體來講，呢部小型 SUV 適合小家庭日常代步的電動車，尤其喺市區駕駛時好靈活，操控輕鬆，外觀時尚，很適合作為油轉電的第一台電動車。</p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299051" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_154156-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_154156-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_154156.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>ALFA ROMEO JUNIOR </strong><strong>規格表</strong><strong>:</strong></p><p>售價: $359,800( Launch Edition) / $429,800 (Sport Edition)</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-1299031 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/alfaromeojuniorhkspe-675x900.jpg" alt="" width="675" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/alfaromeojuniorhkspe.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/alfaromeojuniorhkspe-435x580.jpg 435w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 675px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
